{"content":[{"data":{"color":"black","source":"The Narrator","time_period":["0s AD"],"unique_sources":["Paul"]},"nodes":[{"type":"prose","nodes":[{"marks":[{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"chapter"}],"object":"leaf","text":"4"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"1"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Therefore, since God in his mercy has given us this new way,* we never give up. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"2"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"2"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"2"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"We reject all shameful deeds and underhanded methods. We don’t try to trick anyone or distort the word of God. We tell the truth before God, and all who are honest know this. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"3"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"3"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"3"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"If the Good News we preach is hidden behind a veil, it is hidden only from people who are perishing. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"4"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"4"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"4"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Satan, who is the god of this world, has blinded the minds of those who don’t believe. They are unable to see the glorious light of the Good News. They don’t understand this message about the glory of Christ, who is the exact likeness of God. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"5"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"5"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"5"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"You see, we don’t go around preaching about ourselves. We preach that Jesus Christ is Lord, and we ourselves are your servants for Jesus’ sake. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"6"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"6"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"6"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"For God, who said, “Let there be light in the darkness,” has made this light shine in our hearts so we could know the glory of God that is seen in the face of Jesus Christ. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"7"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"7"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"7"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"We now have this light shining in our hearts, but we ourselves are like fragile clay jars containing this great treasure.* This makes it clear that our great power is from God, not from ourselves. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"8"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"8"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"8"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"We are pressed on every side by troubles, but we are not crushed. We are perplexed, but not driven to despair. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"9"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"9"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"9"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"We are hunted down, but never abandoned by God. We get knocked down, but we are not destroyed. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"10"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"10"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"10"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Through suffering, our bodies continue to share in the death of Jesus so that the life of Jesus may also be seen in our bodies. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"11"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"11"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"11"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Yes, we live under constant danger of death because we serve Jesus, so that the life of Jesus will be evident in our dying bodies. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"12"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"12"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"12"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"So we live in the face of death, but this has resulted in eternal life for you. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"13"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"13"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"13"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"But we continue to preach because we have the same kind of faith the psalmist had when he said, “I believed in God, so I spoke.”* "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"14"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"14"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"14"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"We know that God, who raised the Lord Jesus,* will also raise us with Jesus and present us to himself together with you. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"15"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"15"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"15"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"All of this is for your benefit. And as God’s grace reaches more and more people, there will be great thanksgiving, and God will receive more and more glory. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"16"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"16"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"16"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"That is why we never give up. Though our bodies are dying, our spirits are* being renewed every day. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"17"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"17"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"17"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"For our present troubles are small and won’t last very long. Yet they produce for us a glory that vastly outweighs them and will last forever! "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"18"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"18"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"4","verse":"18"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"So we don’t look at the troubles we can see now; rather, we fix our gaze on things that cannot be seen. For the things we see now will soon be gone, but the things we cannot see will last forever. "},{"marks":[{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"\n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"chapter"}],"object":"leaf","text":"5"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"1"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"For we know that when this earthly tent we live in is taken down (that is, when we die and leave this earthly body), we will have a house in heaven, an eternal body made for us by God himself and not by human hands. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"2"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"2"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"2"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"We grow weary in our present bodies, and we long to put on our heavenly bodies like new clothing. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"3"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"3"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"3"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"For we will put on heavenly bodies; we will not be spirits without bodies.* "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"4"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"4"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"4"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"While we live in these earthly bodies, we groan and sigh, but it’s not that we want to die and get rid of these bodies that clothe us. Rather, we want to put on our new bodies so that these dying bodies will be swallowed up by life. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"5"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"5"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"5"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"God himself has prepared us for this, and as a guarantee he has given us his Holy Spirit. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"6"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"6"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"6"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"So we are always confident, even though we know that as long as we live in these bodies we are not at home with the Lord. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"7"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"7"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"7"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"For we live by believing and not by seeing. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"8"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"8"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"8"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Yes, we are fully confident, and we would rather be away from these earthly bodies, for then we will be at home with the Lord. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"9"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"9"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"9"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"So whether we are here in this body or away from this body, our goal is to please him. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"10"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"10"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"10"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"For we must all stand before Christ to be judged. We will each receive whatever we deserve for the good or evil we have done in this earthly body. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"11"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"11"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"11"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Because we understand our fearful responsibility to the Lord, we work hard to persuade others. God knows we are sincere, and I hope you know this, too. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"12"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"12"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"12"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Are we commending ourselves to you again? No, we are giving you a reason to be proud of us,* so you can answer those who brag about having a spectacular ministry rather than having a sincere heart. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"13"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"13"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"13"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"If it seems we are crazy, it is to bring glory to God. And if we are in our right minds, it is for your benefit. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"14"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"14"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"14"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Either way, Christ’s love controls us.* Since we believe that Christ died for all, we also believe that we have all died to our old life.* "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"15"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"15"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"15"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"He died for everyone so that those who receive his new life will no longer live for themselves. Instead, they will live for Christ, who died and was raised for them. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"16"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"16"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"16"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"So we have stopped evaluating others from a human point of view. At one time we thought of Christ merely from a human point of view. How differently we know him now! "},{"marks":[{"data":{"id":"FOU-26"},"object":"mark","type":"keyPassage"},{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"17"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"17"},{"marks":[{"data":{"id":"FOU-26"},"object":"mark","type":"keyPassage"},{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"17"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"This means that anyone who belongs to Christ has become a new person. The old life is gone; a new life has begun!"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"17"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":" \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"18"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"},{"data":{"id":"REL-02"},"object":"mark","type":"keyPassage"}],"object":"leaf","text":"18"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"18"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"data":{"id":"REL-02"},"object":"mark","type":"keyPassage"}],"object":"leaf","text":"And all of this is a gift from God, who brought us back to himself through Christ. And God has given us this task of reconciling people to him. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"19"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"},{"data":{"id":"REL-02"},"object":"mark","type":"keyPassage"}],"object":"leaf","text":"19"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"19"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"data":{"id":"REL-02"},"object":"mark","type":"keyPassage"}],"object":"leaf","text":"For God was in Christ, reconciling the world to himself, no longer counting people’s sins against them. And he gave us this wonderful message of reconciliation. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"20"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"},{"data":{"id":"REL-02"},"object":"mark","type":"keyPassage"}],"object":"leaf","text":"20"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"20"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"data":{"id":"REL-02"},"object":"mark","type":"keyPassage"}],"object":"leaf","text":"So we are Christ’s ambassadors; God is making his appeal through us. We speak for Christ when we plead, “Come back to God!”"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"20"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":" "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"21"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"21"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"5","verse":"21"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"For God made Christ, who never sinned, to be the offering for our sin,* so that we could be made right with God through Christ. "},{"marks":[{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"\n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"chapter"}],"object":"leaf","text":"6"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"1"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"As God’s partners,* we beg you not to accept this marvelous gift of God’s kindness and then ignore it. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"2"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"2"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"2"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"For God says,\n“At just the right time, I heard you. \nOn the day of salvation, I helped you.”*\nIndeed, the “right time” is now. Today is the day of salvation. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"3"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"3"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"3"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"We live in such a way that no one will stumble because of us, and no one will find fault with our ministry. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"4"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"4"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"4"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"In everything we do, we show that we are true ministers of God. We patiently endure troubles and hardships and calamities of every kind. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"5"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"5"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"5"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"We have been beaten, been put in prison, faced angry mobs, worked to exhaustion, endured sleepless nights, and gone without food. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"6"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"6"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"6"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"We prove ourselves by our purity, our understanding, our patience, our kindness, by the Holy Spirit within us,* and by our sincere love. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"7"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"7"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"7"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"We faithfully preach the truth. God’s power is working in us. We use the weapons of righteousness in the right hand for attack and the left hand for defense. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"8"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"8"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"8"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"We serve God whether people honor us or despise us, whether they slander us or praise us. We are honest, but they call us impostors. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"9"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"9"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"9"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"We are ignored, even though we are well known. We live close to death, but we are still alive. We have been beaten, but we have not been killed. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"10"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"10"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"10"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Our hearts ache, but we always have joy. We are poor, but we give spiritual riches to others. We own nothing, and yet we have everything. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"11"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"11"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"11"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Oh, dear Corinthian friends! We have spoken honestly with you, and our hearts are open to you. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"12"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"12"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"12"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"There is no lack of love on our part, but you have withheld your love from us. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"13"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"13"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"13"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"I am asking you to respond as if you were my own children. Open your hearts to us! \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"14"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"14"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"14"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Don’t team up with those who are unbelievers. How can righteousness be a partner with wickedness? How can light live with darkness? "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"15"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"15"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"15"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"What harmony can there be between Christ and the devil*? How can a believer be a partner with an unbeliever? "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"16"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"16"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"16"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"And what union can there be between God’s temple and idols? For we are the temple of the living God. As God said:\n“I will live in them \nand walk among them. \nI will be their God, \nand they will be my people.* \n"}]},{"type":"poetry","nodes":[{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"object":"mark","type":"poetry"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"17"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"17"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"object":"mark","type":"poetry"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"17"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Therefore, come out from among unbelievers, \nand separate yourselves from them, says the Lord. \nDon’t touch their filthy things, \nand I will welcome you.* \n"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"object":"mark","type":"poetry"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"18"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"18"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"object":"mark","type":"poetry"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"6","verse":"18"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"And I will be your Father, \nand you will be my sons and daughters, \nsays the Lord Almighty.*” "}]},{"type":"prose","nodes":[{"marks":[{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"chapter"}],"object":"leaf","text":"7"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"1"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"1"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Because we have these promises, dear friends, let us cleanse ourselves from everything that can defile our body or spirit. And let us work toward complete holiness because we fear God. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"2"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"2"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"2"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Please open your hearts to us. We have not done wrong to anyone, nor led anyone astray, nor taken advantage of anyone. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"3"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"3"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"3"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"I’m not saying this to condemn you. I said before that you are in our hearts, and we live or die together with you. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"4"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"4"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"4"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"I have the highest confidence in you, and I take great pride in you. You have greatly encouraged me and made me happy despite all our troubles. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"5"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"5"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"5"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"When we arrived in Macedonia, there was no rest for us. We faced conflict from every direction, with battles on the outside and fear on the inside. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"6"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"6"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"6"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"But God, who encourages those who are discouraged, encouraged us by the arrival of Titus. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"7"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"7"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"7"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"His presence was a joy, but so was the news he brought of the encouragement he received from you. When he told us how much you long to see me, and how sorry you are for what happened, and how loyal you are to me, I was filled with joy! \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"8"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"8"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"8"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"I am not sorry that I sent that severe letter to you, though I was sorry at first, for I know it was painful to you for a little while. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"9"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"9"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"9"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Now I am glad I sent it, not because it hurt you, but because the pain caused you to repent and change your ways. It was the kind of sorrow God wants his people to have, so you were not harmed by us in any way. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"10"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"10"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"10"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"For the kind of sorrow God wants us to experience leads us away from sin and results in salvation. There’s no regret for that kind of sorrow. But worldly sorrow, which lacks repentance, results in spiritual death. \n\t"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"11"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"11"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"11"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Just see what this godly sorrow produced in you! Such earnestness, such concern to clear yourselves, such indignation, such alarm, such longing to see me, such zeal, and such a readiness to punish wrong. You showed that you have done everything necessary to make things right. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"12"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"12"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"12"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"My purpose, then, was not to write about who did the wrong or who was wronged. I wrote to you so that in the sight of God you could see for yourselves how loyal you are to us. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"13"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"13"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"13"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"We have been greatly encouraged by this.\n\tIn addition to our own encouragement, we were especially delighted to see how happy Titus was about the way all of you welcomed him and set his mind* at ease. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"14"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"14"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"14"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"I had told him how proud I was of you—and you didn’t disappoint me. I have always told you the truth, and now my boasting to Titus has also proved true! "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"15"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"15"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"15"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"Now he cares for you more than ever when he remembers the way all of you obeyed him and welcomed him with such fear and deep respect. "},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"16"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"},{"object":"mark","type":"verse"}],"object":"leaf","text":"16"},{"marks":[{"object":"mark","type":"literature"},{"data":{"book":"2Co","chapter":"7","verse":"16"},"object":"mark","type":"reference"}],"object":"leaf","text":"I am very happy now because I have complete confidence in you. "}]}]}],"colors":{"total":1968,"black":1968,"red":0,"green":0,"blue":0},"repeatedWords":["us (34)","our (30)","God (33)","have (22)","Christ (14)","bodies (14)","live (13)","has (10)","all (9)","life (8)","know (8)","can (8)","such (8)","Jesus (8)","ourselves (7)","hearts (7)","Lord (7)","because (7)","way (6)","body (6)"],"sources":{"The Narrator":{"words":1968,"color":"black"}},"id":"S332"}